summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Neighborhoods; authorizing a grant agreement with the State of Washington Department of Natural Resources, accepting Aquatic Lands Enhancement Account (ALEA) funds; authorizing a letter of agreement with the Port of Seattle accepting funds; authorizing use of funds for preparation of a schematic design for the Alki/Harbor/Duwamish corridor; and making reimbursable appropriations from the General Fund; all by a three-fourths vote of the City Council.
